Title: Dedicates a portion of the state highway system to "Emmaline 'Emma' Wilcox"
Summary: Dedicates the portion of state route 60 between Shumla Road and Lakeview Road in the town of Stockton, county of Chautauqua, to "Emmaline 'Emma' Wilcox".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to dedicating a portion of the state highway system to "Emmaline 'Emma' Wilcox"
